<lb ed="GA" n="b117a13"/>逸者出堂</item>
<lb ed="GA" n="b117a14"/><item xml:id="itemGA056pb117a1401"><note n="b117a1401" resp="CBETA" type="add">〔－〕【CB】，一【志彙】</note><app n="b117a1401"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【志彙】">一</rdg></app>聽經須解義若不解義庶無悟期隨行逐隊虛應故事者出堂</item>
