<lb ed="GA" n="b120a05"/><item xml:id="itemGA056pb120a0501"><note n="b120a0501" resp="CBETA" type="add">〔－〕【CB】，一【志彙】</note><app n="b120a0501"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【志彙】">一</rdg></app>厨房高聲大叫者罰飲酒賭博者重罰出院</item>
